{{Top|leg|canon=Gyro-balance system}}
'''Gyro-balance circuitry ''' provided machines with three-dimensional direction-sensing capabilities. The devices were found in [[Droid/Legends|droids]]&mdash;as the part of the [[Behavioral circuitry matrix/Legends|behavioral circuitry matrix]]&mdash;and vehicles, giving them stability in all three planes.

